{"tid":2460424,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登內閣缺乏亞裔要員 遭民主黨黨友「逼宮」","createTime":"2021-03-24T23:36:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T05:58:24.000Z","uid":130626,"like":14,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ea745ab71c49e8997be127e1c0f2f7a41ebe281c","tid":2460424,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T23:36:34.000Z","msg":"美國參議院正投票任命多位新政府內閣人選，周二，兩名民主黨參議員對提名人選投反對票，原因是拜登總統內閣缺乏足夠亞裔代表。白宮晚上表示，同意增加一名美藉亞裔人士或太平洋島民（AAPI），加入內閣擔任重要職位。<br />\n<br />\n白宮發言人普薩基（Jen Psaki）在聲明中指，拜登已明確表示，新政府班底將反映國家多元民族，這一直是他們的目標，因此將增加一名亞裔人士擔任要職，代表不同族群聲音。不過，白宮沒有透露誰人將擔任這個職位，或職位是否新設等問題。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210325/JRNSKGJRCBEUVEBVCPJPYV7BVI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210325%2FJRNSKGJRCBEUVEBVCPJPYV7BVI%2F&d=G6FzB8XOFkGMVaf%2BSD5%2FxqhYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=6ced4d66\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210325%2FJRNSKGJRCBEUVEBVCPJPYV7BVI%2F&h=aa9209b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210325/JRNSKGJRCBEUVEBVCPJPYV7BVI/</a>"},{"pid":"4701cc8522010793107b0afc8ada6b83e8973f1f","tid":2460424,"uid":3457,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T23:38:45.000Z","msg":"副總統唔係亞裔咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffeb61e4ef43225bd8d6c092f087446cb7f0679e","tid":2460424,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T23:38:46.000Z","msg":"習近平見到唔發你圍就假啦"},{"pid":"4bce6b70ac33c0e0a8e3e5b61daf0b71e36f0942","tid":2460424,"uid":511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4701cc8522010793107b0afc8ada6b83e8973f1f","tid":2460424,"uid":3457,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T23:38:45.000Z","msg":"副總統唔係亞裔咩<img 